452
00:26:50,189 --> 00:26:53,784
<i>Third down and 6. Guards have
the ball on their own 29-yard line.</i>

453
00:26:53,993 --> 00:26:56,461
<i>Knauer needs a first down
to put this game away.</i>

454
00:26:56,662 --> 00:26:58,129
White 50!

455
00:26:58,731 --> 00:26:59,789
White 50!

456
00:26:59,999 --> 00:27:02,160
<i>And look at Battle take off.</i>

457
00:27:03,569 --> 00:27:05,036
<i>He knocks the ball loose!</i>

458
00:27:06,305 --> 00:27:10,867
<i>There's a dogpile in the backfield.
